<div class="container p-5">
  <div class="col-12 text-center mb-5">
    <div class="webnair-section4_title display-2 text-dark fw-semibold">KEY TAKEAWAYS</div>
  </div>

  <div class="col-12">
    <ul class="webnair-section_content mb-5">
      <li class="fs-2 text-dark mb-3">
        🫁 <span class="fw-bold">Respiratory Insights:</span> Dr. Rajakumar unveils the inner workings of your lungs,
        helping you grasp the fundamentals of respiratory health.
      </li>
      <li class="fs-2 text-dark mb-3">
        🌬️ <span class="fw-bold">Empowering Knowledge:</span> Gain a deeper understanding of common respiratory
        challenges, from asthma to allergies, and learn to spot early warning signs.
      </li>

      <li class="fs-2 text-dark mb-3">
        🌟 <span class="fw-bold">Expert Guidance:</span> Receive valuable advice from Dr. Rajakumar on managing chronic
        respiratory conditions, reducing stress, and improving overall well-being.
      </li>

      <li class="fs-2 text-dark mb-3">
        📚 <span class="fw-bold">Health Education:</span> Access a wealth of knowledge and resources to help you and
        your loved ones breathe easier and live life to the fullest.
      </li>

      <li class="fs-2 text-dark mb-3">
        📚 <span class="fw-bold">AMA Session:</span> Join Dr. Rajakumar for an interactive Q&A session, where you can
        get personalised insights and answers to their respiratory health concerns.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <div class="mb-5 text-center">
      {% form 'product', product %}
        <div>
          <input
            type="hidden"
            name="id"
            value="{{ product.variants.first.id }}"
          >
          <input
            type="hidden"
            name="quantity"
            value="1"
          >
          <button
            onclick="window.zecpeCheckFunctionAndCall ? window.zecpeCheckFunctionAndCall('ZecpeCheckVariant', this) : window.location.href = '/cart/checkout'; event.stopPropagation(); event.stopImmediatePropagation();"
            class="btn buy-now-button"
          >
            Reserve Your Seat Now!
          </button>
        </div>
      {% endform %}
      <div class="text-dark fs-4 mt-2 fw-medium">{{ product.metafields.custom.webnair_date_time }}</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="col-12">
    <div class="webnair-section_content text-center">
      <div class="fs-1 text-dark fw-semibold webnair-section4_title-bg">
        To <span>bridge this gap</span> and promote a healthier community, BIBO Health is hosting a webinar featuring
        <span>Dr. Rajkumar</span>, a renowned expert in pulmonary health.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

